# Benchmark provenance: metadata and READMEs ARE tracked,
# parquet/joblib/JSON results are not. Git negation requires
# unignoring each parent directory along the path.
!data/
data/raw/
data/interim/
data/external/
!data/processed/
data/processed/*
!data/processed/benchmarks/
!data/processed/benchmarks/**
data/processed/benchmarks/**/*.parquet
data/processed/benchmarks/**/*.joblib
data/processed/benchmarks/**/*.csv
data/processed/benchmarks/**/eval_*.json
data/processed/benchmarks/**/split_summary.json

